  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Diospaj llank'asaj Señor Jesuswan,
 Janaj pachaman Paywan rinaypaj./
 
[C]
 /Gloria kachun Señor Jesusman,
 Janaj pachapeqa Paywan kawsasaj./
 
[V2]
 /Señor Jesusqa juchasniyrayku
 Chay k'aspi cruzpi Pay ñak’arerqa./
 
[V3]
 /Jaqay cielopi fikas chawpipi
 Qori arpaspi Pay man takisaj./
 
[V4]
 /Señor Jesuswan noqa kawsasaj
 Wiñay wiñaypaj janaj pachapi./
 
</lyrics></song>